text: Noah Kahan ( ; born January 1, 1997) is an American singer-songwriter. He is known for his single "Hurt Somebody". His first album, Busyhead came out in 2019. He then released the albums I Was / I Am (2021) and Stick Season (2022). ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:American singer-songwriters Category:American pop singers Category:American folk singers Category:American guitarists Category:Musicians from Vermont Category:Writers from Vermont Category:Singers from Vermont Category:People from Hanover, New Hampshire Category:Musicians from New Hampshire Category:Singers from New Hampshire Category:Writers from New Hampshire
